<br>
Best advice is to just practice to where you can use both of your characters very fast, if you have a hard time with keyboards and have to look at keys and can't tell from feel then you probably won't have too good of a time.  Need fast hand eye coordination.  I myself usually play Warrior (main cause I pull and am the assist), Wizard (off comp), or Cleric-main / Wizard-off or.  Or other combos, but I always try to keep a lax character on my off computer that I don't need to worry about too much.  Wizard is perfect cause all you really need to do is snare and lay some timely nukes.  There is more to this class yes, but for the most part it can be done very easily with just one hand.<br>
